library AWATestComposite version '0.0.008'

using QDM version '5.4'

include CompositeFunctions version '0.1.000' called Composite
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCarePneumococcalVaccination version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasurePneumococcal
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforColorectalCancer version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureColorectal
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforDepression version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureDepression
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforFallsRisk version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureFalls
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforOsteoporosis version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareInfluenzaVaccination version '0.4.000' called ComponentMeasureInfluenza
include AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforBreastCancer version '0.5.000' called ComponentMeasureBreast

valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Denominator":
	ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Numerator":
	ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureColorectal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureDepression."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureDepression."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureFalls."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureFalls."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureFalls."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator"
		and not ( ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator Exceptions"
				and not ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Numerator"
		)

define "Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator"
		and ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Numerator"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureColorectal."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureDepression."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exclusions"
		and not ( ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exceptions"
				and not ComponentMeasureDepression."Numerator"
		)

define "Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Denominator":
	ComponentMeasureBreast."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator Exclusions"

define "Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Numerator":
	ComponentMeasureBreast."Initial Population"
		and ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator"
		and not ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator Exclusions"
		and ComponentMeasureBreast."Numerator"

define "Initial Population":
	["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Pt
		where ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureColorectal."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureDepression."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureFalls."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Initial Population"
			or ComponentMeasureBreast."Initial Population"

define "Measure Population":
	["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Pt
		where ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureInfluenza."Denominator"
			or ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator"

define "Numerator Score":
	Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Numerator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Numerator")

define "Denominator Score":
	Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasurePneumococcal Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureColorectal Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureDepression Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureFalls Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureInfluenza Denominator")+ Composite.ToScore("Is In ComponentMeasureBreast Denominator")

define "Measure Population Exclusions":
	["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Pt
		where ComponentMeasurePneumococcal."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureColorectal."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureDepression."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureFalls."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureOsteoporosis."Denominator Exclusions"
			and ComponentMeasureBreast."Denominator Exclusions"

define function "Measure Observation"(patient "Patient Characteristic Birthdate"):
	"Numerator Score" / "Denominator Score"

library AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCarePneumococcalVaccination version '0.4.000'

using QDM version '5.4'

include MATGlobalCommonFunctions version '4.0.000' called Global
include Hospice version '2.0.000' called Hospice

valueset "Annual Wellness Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1240'
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Pneumococcal Vaccine": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.110.12.1027'
valueset "Pneumococcal Vaccine Administered": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.110.12.1034'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Denominator":
	"Initial Population"

define "Numerator":
	exists ( ["Immunization, Administered": "Pneumococcal Vaccine"] PneumococcalVaccine
			where PneumococcalVaccine.authorDatetime on or before 
			end of "Measurement Period"
	)
		or exists ( ["Procedure, Performed": "Pneumococcal Vaccine Administered"] PneumococcalVaccineGiven
				where PneumococcalVaccineGiven.relevantPeriod starts on or before 
				end of "Measurement Period"
		)

define "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Annual Wellness Visit"] QualifyingEncounter
		where QualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Initial Population":
	exists ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
		where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
			and exists "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"

define "Denominator Exclusions":
	Hospice."Has Hospice"

library Hospice version '2.0.000'

using QDM version '5.4'

codesystem "SNOMEDCT:2017-09": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96' version 'urn:hl7:version:2017-09'

valueset "Encounter Inpatient": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.666.5.307' 
valueset "Hospice care ambulatory": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1108.15' 

code "Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)": '428371000124100' from "SNOMEDCT:2017-09" display 'Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)'
code "Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)": '428361000124107' from "SNOMEDCT:2017-09" display 'Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "Has Hospice":
	exists ( ["Encounter, Performed": "Encounter Inpatient"] DischargeHospice
			where ( DischargeHospice.dischargeDisposition as Code ~ "Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)"
					or DischargeHospice.dischargeDisposition as Code ~ "Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)"
			)
				and DischargeHospice.relevantPeriod ends during "Measurement Period"
	)
		or exists ( ["Intervention, Order": "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospiceOrder
				where HospiceOrder.authorDatetime during "Measurement Period"
		)
		or exists ( ["Intervention, Performed": "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospicePerformed
				where HospicePerformed.relevantPeriod overlaps "Measurement Period"
		)

library MATGlobalCommonFunctions version '4.0.000'

using QDM version '5.4'

valueset "Emergency Department Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.117.1.7.1.292' 
valueset "Encounter Inpatient": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.666.5.307' 
valueset "Intensive Care Unit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1110.23' 

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Emergency Department Visit"]

define "Inpatient Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Encounter Inpatient"] EncounterInpatient
		where "LengthInDays"(EncounterInpatient.relevantPeriod)<= 120
			and EncounterInpatient.relevantPeriod ends during "Measurement Period"

/*ToDate takes a given DateTime value and returns a DateTime with the time components "zeroed", and the timezone of the input value, for example, given the DateTime @2012-01-01T06:30:00.0Z, this function will return @2012-01-01T00:00:00.0Z.*/
define function "ToDate"(Value DateTime ):
	DateTime(year from Value, month from Value, day from Value, 0, 0, 0, 0, timezone from Value)

/*CalendarAgeInDaysAt calculates the calendar age (meaning the age without considering time components) in days.*/
define function "CalendarAgeInDaysAt"(BirthDateTime DateTime, AsOf DateTime ):
	days between ToDate(BirthDateTime)and ToDate(AsOf)

/*CalendarAgeInDays calculates the calendar age (meaning the age without considering time components) in days as of today*/
define function "CalendarAgeInDays"(BirthDateTime DateTime ):
	CalendarAgeInDaysAt(BirthDateTime, Today())

/*CalendarAgeInMonthsAt calculates the calendar age (meaning the age without considering time components) in months.*/
define function "CalendarAgeInMonthsAt"(BirthDateTime DateTime, AsOf DateTime ):
	months between ToDate(BirthDateTime)and ToDate(AsOf)

/*CalendarAgeInMonths calculates the calendar age (meaning the age without considering time components) in months as of today.*/
define function "CalendarAgeInMonths"(BirthDateTime DateTime ):
	CalendarAgeInMonthsAt(BirthDateTime, Today())

/*CalendarAgeInYearsAt calculates the calendar age (meaning the age without considering time components) in years.*/
define function "CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDateTime DateTime, AsOf DateTime ):
	years between ToDate(BirthDateTime)and ToDate(AsOf)

/*CalendarAgeInYears calculates the calendar age (meaning the age without considering time components) in years as of today.*/
define function "CalendarAgeInYears"(BirthDateTime DateTime ):
	CalendarAgeInYearsAt(BirthDateTime, Today())

/*Hospitalization returns the total interval for admission to discharge for the given encounter, or for the admission of any immediately prior emergency department visit to the discharge of the given encounter.*/
define function "Hospitalization"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	( singleton from ( ["Encounter, Performed": "Emergency Department Visit"] EDVisit
			where EDVisit.relevantPeriod ends 1 hour or less on or before start of Encounter.relevantPeriod
	) ) X
		return if X is null then Encounter.relevantPeriod else Interval[start of X.relevantPeriod, end of Encounter.relevantPeriod]

/*calculates the difference in calendar days between the start and end of the given interval.*/
define function "LengthInDays"(Value Interval<DateTime> ):
	difference in days between start of Value and end of Value

/* returns list of all locations within an encounter, including locations for immediately prior ED visit.  If data contains many encounters within 1 hour before the start of encounter error will occur indicating the hospitalization cannot be determined*/
define function "Hospitalization Locations"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	( singleton from ( ["Encounter, Performed": "Emergency Department Visit"] EDVisit
			where EDVisit.relevantPeriod ends 1 hour or less on or before start of Encounter.relevantPeriod
	) ) EDEncounter
		return if EDEncounter is null then Encounter.facilityLocations else flatten { EDEncounter.facilityLocations, Encounter.facilityLocations }

/*Returns the length of stay in days (i.e. the number of days between admission and discharge) for the given encounter, or from the admission of any immediately prior emergency department visit to the discharge of the encounter*/
define function "Hospitalization Length of Stay"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	LengthInDays("Hospitalization"(Encounter))

/*Returns admission time for an encounter or for immediately prior emergency department visit.  If the data contain many encounters within 1 hour before the start of the encounter an error indicating hospitalization cannot be determined
*/
define function "Hospital Admission Time"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	start of "Hospitalization"(Encounter)

/*Hospital Discharge Time returns the discharge time for an encounter*/
define function "Hospital Discharge Time"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	end of Encounter.relevantPeriod

/*Returns earliest arrival time for an encounter including any prior ED visit. If the data contain multiple encounters within 1 hour before the start of the encounter, an error will occur indicating it cannot be unambiguously determined
*/
define function "Hospital Arrival Time"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	start of First(("Hospitalization Locations"(Encounter))HospitalLocation
			sort by start of locationPeriod
	).locationPeriod

/*Returns the latest departure time for encounter including any prior ED visit. If the data contain multiple encounters within 1 hour before the start of the encounter, an error will occur indicating it cannot be unambiguously determined*/
define function "Hospital Departure Time"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	end of Last(("Hospitalization Locations"(Encounter))HospitalLocation
			sort by start of locationPeriod
	).locationPeriod

/*Returns the arrival time in the ED for the encounter.  If the data contain multiple encounters within 1 hour before the start of the encounter or multiple ED locations an error will occur indicating it cannot be determined
*/
define function "Emergency Department Arrival Time"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	start of ( singleton from ( ( "Hospitalization Locations"(Encounter)) HospitalLocation
				where HospitalLocation.code in "Emergency Department Visit"
		)
	).locationPeriod

/*First Inpatient Intensive Care Unit returns the first intensive care unit for
the given encounter, without considering any immediately prior emergency
department visit.*/
define function "First Inpatient Intensive Care Unit"(Encounter "Encounter, Performed" ):
	First((Encounter.facilityLocations)HospitalLocation
			where HospitalLocation.code in "Intensive Care Unit"
				and HospitalLocation.locationPeriod during Encounter.relevantPeriod
			sort by start of locationPeriod
	)

library AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforColorectalCancer version '0.4.000'

using QDM version '5.4'

include Hospice version '2.0.000' called Hospice
include MATGlobalCommonFunctions version '4.0.000' called Global

valueset "Annual Wellness Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1240'
valueset "Colonoscopy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.108.12.1020'
valueset "CT Colonography": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.108.12.1038'
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "Fecal Occult Blood Test (FOBT)": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1011'
valueset "FIT DNA": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.108.12.1039'
valueset "Flexible Sigmoidoscopy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1010'
valueset "Malignant Neoplasm of Colon": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.108.12.1001'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'
valueset "Total Colectomy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1019'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Colonoscopy Performed":
	["Procedure, Performed": "Colonoscopy"] Colonoscopy
		where Colonoscopy.relevantPeriod ends 10 years or less on or before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "CT Colonography Performed":
	["Procedure, Performed": "CT Colonography"] Colonography
		where Colonography.relevantPeriod ends 5 years or less on or before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Malignant Neoplasm":
	["Diagnosis": "Malignant Neoplasm of Colon"] ColorectalCancer
		where ColorectalCancer.prevalencePeriod starts on or before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Fecal Occult Blood Test Performed":
	["Laboratory Test, Performed": "Fecal Occult Blood Test (FOBT)"] FecalOccultResult
		where FecalOccultResult.result is not null
			and FecalOccultResult.authorDatetime during "Measurement Period"

define "Flexible Sigmoidoscopy Performed":
	["Procedure, Performed": "Flexible Sigmoidoscopy"] FlexibleSigmoidoscopy
		where FlexibleSigmoidoscopy.relevantPeriod ends 5 years or less on or before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Fecal Immunochemical Test DNA Performed":
	["Laboratory Test, Performed": "FIT DNA"] FitDNA
		where FitDNA.result is not null
			and FitDNA.authorDatetime occurs 3 years or less on or before 
			end of "Measurement Period"

define "Numerator":
	exists "Colonoscopy Performed"
		or exists "Fecal Occult Blood Test Performed"
		or exists "Flexible Sigmoidoscopy Performed"
		or exists "Fecal Immunochemical Test DNA Performed"
		or exists "CT Colonography Performed"

define "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Annual Wellness Visit"] QualifyingEncounter
		where QualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Initial Population":
	exists ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
		where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
			and exists "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"

define "Total Colectomy Performed":
	["Procedure, Performed": "Total Colectomy"] Colectomy
		where Colectomy.relevantPeriod starts on or before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Denominator":
	"Initial Population"
		and exists ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
			where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")< 75

define "Denominator Exclusions":
	Hospice."Has Hospice"
		or exists "Malignant Neoplasm"
		or exists "Total Colectomy Performed"

library AnnualWellnessAssessmentPreventiveCareScreeningforDepression version '0.4.000'

using QDM version '5.4'

include MATGlobalCommonFunctions version '4.0.000' called Global

codesystem "LOINC": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.1'

valueset "Adult Depression Screening": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.2449'
valueset "Annual Wellness Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1240'
valueset "Bipolar Diagnosis": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.450'
valueset "Depression diagnosis": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.145'
valueset "Depression Screening  Encounter Codes": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.1916'
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "Medical or Other reason not done": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.1.1502'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Patient Reason refused": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.600.791'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'

code "Birthdate": '21112-8' from "LOINC" display 'Birthdate'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Denominator":
	"Initial Population"

define "Initial Population":
	exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Birthdate
			where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(Birthdate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
	)
		and exists "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"

define "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Annual Wellness Visit"] QualifyingEncounter
		where QualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Depression Screening Encounter within 12 Months Prior to AWV":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Depression Screening  Encounter Codes"] OtherQualifyingEncounter
		with "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessEncounter
			such that OtherQualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod 12 months or less on or before day of 
			end of WellnessEncounter.relevantPeriod

define "Numerator":
	exists ( ["Assessment, Performed": "Adult Depression Screening"] DepressionScreening
			with ( "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"
				union "Depression Screening Encounter within 12 Months Prior to AWV" ) AllQualifyingEncounters
				such that DepressionScreening.authorDatetime during AllQualifyingEncounters.relevantPeriod
	)

define "Has Diagnosis of Bipolar":
	["Diagnosis": "Bipolar Diagnosis"] Bipolar
		with "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessEncounter
			such that Bipolar.prevalencePeriod overlaps before WellnessEncounter.relevantPeriod

define "Has Diagnosis of Depression":
	["Diagnosis": "Depression diagnosis"] Depression
		with "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessEncounter
			such that Depression.prevalencePeriod overlaps before WellnessEncounter.relevantPeriod

define "Has No Depression Screening Due to Medical Reason":
	exists ["Assessment, Not Performed": "Medical or Other reason not done"] MedicalReason
		with ( "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"
			union "Depression Screening Encounter within 12 Months Prior to AWV" ) AllQualifyingEncounters
			such that MedicalReason.negationRationale in "Medical or Other reason not done"
				and MedicalReason.authorDatetime during AllQualifyingEncounters.relevantPeriod

define "Has No Depression Screening Due to Patient Refusal":
	exists ["Assessment, Not Performed": "Patient Reason refused"] PatientReason
		with ( "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"
			union "Depression Screening Encounter within 12 Months Prior to AWV" ) AllQualifyingEncounters
			such that PatientReason.negationRationale in "Patient Reason refused"
				and PatientReason.authorDatetime during AllQualifyingEncounters.relevantPeriod

define "Denominator Exceptions":

using QDM version '5.4'

include MATGlobalCommonFunctions version '4.0.000' called Global

codesystem "LOINC": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.1'
codesystem "SNOMEDCT:2017-09": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.6.96' version 'urn:hl7:version:2017-09'

valueset "Ambulatory Status": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.118.11.1219'
valueset "Annual Wellness Visit": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1240'
valueset "Encounter Inpatient": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.666.5.307'
valueset "Ethnicity": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.837'
valueset "Falls Screening": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.118.12.1028'
valueset "Hospice care ambulatory": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1108.15'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Patient not ambulatory": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.118.12.1009'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'

code "Birthdate": '21112-8' from "LOINC" display 'Birthdate'
code "Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)": '428371000124100' from "SNOMEDCT:2017-09" display 'Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)'
code "Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)": '428361000124107' from "SNOMEDCT:2017-09" display 'Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Denominator":
	"Initial Population"

define "Initial Population":
	exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] Birthdate
			where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(Birthdate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
	)
		and exists "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"

define "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Annual Wellness Visit"] QualifyingEncounter
		where QualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Ambulatory Status Assessed 12 Months Before or During AWV":
	["Assessment, Performed": "Ambulatory Status"] AmbulatoryStatusAssessed
		with "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessVisit
			such that AmbulatoryStatusAssessed.authorDatetime 12 months or less on or before day of 
			end of WellnessVisit.relevantPeriod
				and AmbulatoryStatusAssessed.result is not null

define "Not Ambulatory 12 Months Before or During AWV":
	exists ( "Ambulatory Status Assessed 12 Months Before or During AWV" AmbulatoryStatusAssessed
			where AmbulatoryStatusAssessed.result in "Patient not ambulatory"
	)

define "Hospice 12 Months Before or During AWV":
	exists ( "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessVisit
			with ["Encounter, Performed": "Encounter Inpatient"] DischargeHospice
				such that ( DischargeHospice.dischargeDisposition as Code ~ "Discharge to home for hospice care (procedure)"
						or DischargeHospice.dischargeDisposition as Code ~ "Discharge to healthcare facility for hospice care (procedure)"
				)
					and DischargeHospice.relevantPeriod ends 12 months or less on or before day of 
					end of WellnessVisit.relevantPeriod
	)
		or exists ( "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessVisit
				with ["Intervention, Order": "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospiceOrder
					such that HospiceOrder.authorDatetime 12 months or less on or before day of 
					end of WellnessVisit.relevantPeriod
		)
		or exists ( "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessVisit
				with ["Intervention, Performed": "Hospice care ambulatory"] HospicePerformed
					such that HospicePerformed.relevantPeriod 12 months or less on or before day of 
					end of WellnessVisit.relevantPeriod
		)

define "Not Ambulatory 12 Months or More Before AWV":
	Last(["Assessment, Performed": "Ambulatory Status"] PriorAmbulatoryStatus
			with "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessVisit
				such that PriorAmbulatoryStatus.authorDatetime 12 months or more on or before day of 
				end of WellnessVisit.relevantPeriod
			sort by authorDatetime
	).result in "Patient not ambulatory"

define "Numerator":
	exists ["Assessment, Performed": "Falls Screening"] FallsScreen
		with "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter" WellnessVisit
			such that FallsScreen.authorDatetime 12 months or less on or before day of 
			end of WellnessVisit.relevantPeriod

define "Denominator Exclusions":
	"Not Ambulatory 12 Months Before or During AWV"
		or ( "Not Ambulatory 12 Months or More Before AWV"
				and not exists "Ambulatory Status Assessed 12 Months Before or During AWV"
		)
		or "Hospice 12 Months Before or During AWV"

valueset "Influenza Vaccination": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.402'
valueset "Influenza Vaccination Declined": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1255'
valueset "Influenza Vaccine": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1254'
valueset "Intolerance to Influenza Vaccine": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1257'
valueset "Medical Reason": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1007'
valueset "ONC Administrative Sex": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1'
valueset "Patient Reason": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1008'
valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'

valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'
valueset "System Reason": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.526.3.1009'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year":
	Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 153 days, start of "Measurement Period" + 90 days]

define "Influenza Season":
	Interval[start of "Measurement Period" - 92 days, start of "Measurement Period" + 90 days]

define "Allergy or Intolerance to Influenza Vaccine":
	["Allergy/Intolerance": "Influenza Vaccine"] FluVaccineAllergyIntolerance
		where FluVaccineAllergyIntolerance.prevalencePeriod overlaps after "Influenza Season"

define "Influenza Immunization Administered":
	["Immunization, Administered": "Influenza Vaccine"] AdministeredFluVaccine
		where AdministeredFluVaccine.authorDatetime during "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year"

define "Diagnosis of Allergy to Egg":
	["Diagnosis": "Allergy to Eggs"] EggAllergy
		where EggAllergy.prevalencePeriod overlaps after "Influenza Season"

define "Diagnosis of Allergy to Influenza Vaccine":
	["Diagnosis": "Allergy to Influenza Vaccine"] FluVaccineAllergyDiagnosis
		where FluVaccineAllergyDiagnosis.prevalencePeriod overlaps after "Influenza Season"

define "Diagnosis of Intolerance to Influenza Vaccine":
	["Diagnosis": "Intolerance to Influenza Vaccine"] FluVaccineIntoleranceDiagnosis
		where FluVaccineIntoleranceDiagnosis.prevalencePeriod overlaps after "Influenza Season"

define "Egg Substance Allergy":
	["Allergy/Intolerance": "Egg Substance"] AllergyEggSubstance
		where AllergyEggSubstance.prevalencePeriod overlaps after "Influenza Season"

define "Intolerance of Influenza Vaccination Procedure":
	["Allergy/Intolerance": "Influenza Vaccination"] FluVaccinationIntolerance
		where FluVaccinationIntolerance.prevalencePeriod overlaps after "Influenza Season"

define "Encounter During Influenza Season":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Encounter-Influenza"] FluEncounter
		where FluEncounter.relevantPeriod starts during "Influenza Season"

define "Medical Patient or System Reason for Not Administering Influenza Vaccine":
	["Immunization, Not Administered": "Influenza Vaccine"] NoFluVaccine
		where NoFluVaccine.authorDatetime during "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year"
			and ( NoFluVaccine.negationRationale in "Medical Reason"
					or NoFluVaccine.negationRationale in "Patient Reason"
					or NoFluVaccine.negationRationale in "System Reason"
			)

define "Medical Patient or System Reason for Not Performing Influenza Vaccination":
	["Procedure, Not Performed": "Influenza Vaccination"] NoFluVaccination
		where NoFluVaccination.authorDatetime during "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year"
			and ( NoFluVaccination.negationRationale in "Medical Reason"
					or NoFluVaccination.negationRationale in "Patient Reason"
					or NoFluVaccination.negationRationale in "System Reason"
			)

define "Numerator":
	exists "Influenza Vaccination Procedure"
		or exists "Influenza Immunization Administered"
		or exists "Patient Reported Previous Receipt of Influenza Vaccine"

define "Denominator":
	"Initial Population"
		and exists "Encounter During Influenza Season"

define "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Annual Wellness Visit"] QualifyingEncounter
		where QualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Initial Population":
	exists ( ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
			where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
	)
		and exists "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"

define "Denominator Exceptions":
	exists "Patient Declined Influenza Vaccination"
		or exists "Medical Patient or System Reason for Not Performing Influenza Vaccination"
		or exists "Medical Patient or System Reason for Not Administering Influenza Vaccine"
		or exists "Diagnosis of Allergy to Egg"
		or exists "Egg Substance Allergy"
		or exists "Diagnosis of Allergy to Influenza Vaccine"
		or exists "Diagnosis of Intolerance to Influenza Vaccine"
		or exists "Intolerance of Influenza Vaccination Procedure"
		or exists "Allergy or Intolerance to Influenza Vaccine"

define "Influenza Vaccination Procedure":
	["Procedure, Performed": "Influenza Vaccination"] FluVaccination
		where FluVaccination.relevantPeriod starts during "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year"

define "Patient Declined Influenza Vaccination":
	["Communication, Performed": "Influenza Vaccination Declined"] CommunicateFluVaccinationDeclined
		where CommunicateFluVaccinationDeclined.authorDatetime during "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year"

define "Patient Reported Previous Receipt of Influenza Vaccine":
	["Communication, Performed": "Previous Receipt of Influenza Vaccine"] CommunicatePreviousReceiptFluVaccine
		where CommunicatePreviousReceiptFluVaccine.authorDatetime during "Influenza Season Including August and September of the Prior Year"

valueset "Payer": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.3591'
valueset "Race": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.114222.4.11.836'
valueset "Right": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.122.12.1035'
valueset "Status Post Left Mastectomy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1069'
valueset "Status Post Right Mastectomy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1070'
valueset "Unilateral Mastectomy": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1020'
valueset "Unilateral Mastectomy, Unspecified Laterality": 'urn:oid:2.16.840.1.113883.3.464.1003.198.12.1071'

parameter "Measurement Period" Interval<DateTime>

context Patient

define "SDE Ethnicity":
	["Patient Characteristic Ethnicity": "Ethnicity"]

define "SDE Payer":
	["Patient Characteristic Payer": "Payer"]

define "SDE Race":
	["Patient Characteristic Race": "Race"]

define "SDE Sex":
	["Patient Characteristic Sex": "ONC Administrative Sex"]

define "Bilateral Mastectomy Procedure":
	["Procedure, Performed": "Bilateral Mastectomy"] BilateralMastectomyPerformed
		where BilateralMastectomyPerformed.relevantPeriod ends before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "History Bilateral Mastectomy":
	["Diagnosis": "History of bilateral mastectomy"] BilateralMastectomyHistory
		where BilateralMastectomyHistory.prevalencePeriod starts before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Left Mastectomy":
	( ["Diagnosis": "Status Post Left Mastectomy"]
		union ( ["Diagnosis": "Unilateral Mastectomy, Unspecified Laterality"] UnilateralMastectomyDiagnosis
				where UnilateralMastectomyDiagnosis.anatomicalLocationSite in "Left"
		) ) LeftMastectomy
		where LeftMastectomy.prevalencePeriod starts before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Right Mastectomy":
	( ["Diagnosis": "Status Post Right Mastectomy"]
		union ( ["Diagnosis": "Unilateral Mastectomy, Unspecified Laterality"] UnilateralMastectomyDiagnosis
				where UnilateralMastectomyDiagnosis.anatomicalLocationSite in "Right"
		) ) RightMastectomy
		where RightMastectomy.prevalencePeriod starts before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Numerator":
	exists ( ["Diagnostic Study, Performed": "Mammography"] Mammogram
			where ( Mammogram.relevantPeriod ends 27 months or less before day of 
				end "Measurement Period"
			)
	)

define "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter":
	["Encounter, Performed": "Annual Wellness Visit"] QualifyingEncounter
		where QualifyingEncounter.relevantPeriod during "Measurement Period"

define "Unilateral Mastectomy Procedure":
	["Procedure, Performed": "Unilateral Mastectomy"] UnilateralMastectomy
		where UnilateralMastectomy.relevantPeriod ends before 
		end of "Measurement Period"

define "Initial Population":
	exists ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
		where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")>= 65
			and exists "Annual Wellness Visit Encounter"

define "Denominator":
	"Initial Population"
		and exists ["Patient Characteristic Sex": "Female"]
		and exists ["Patient Characteristic Birthdate"] BirthDate
			where Global."CalendarAgeInYearsAt"(BirthDate.birthDatetime, start of "Measurement Period")<= 74

define "Denominator Exclusions":
	Hospice."Has Hospice"
		or ( Count("Unilateral Mastectomy Procedure")= 2 )
		or ( exists "Right Mastectomy"
				and exists "Left Mastectomy"
		)
		or exists "History Bilateral Mastectomy"
		or exists "Bilateral Mastectomy Procedure"

value: or less before day of end

children.text: or less before day of end
